<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Reset Your Password</h2>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" style="background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">Reset Password</a>
    </p>
    <p>This link will expire in 30 minutes for security reasons.</p>
    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p>{{resetLink}}</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>PayBud Team</p>
</body>
</html>
